headline: POOL Q4 Deep Dive: Flat Sales and Cautious Guidance Amid Ongoing Market Pressure
summary: Swimming pool distributor Pool (NASDAQ:POOL) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales flat year on year at $982.2 million. Its GAAP profit of $0.85 per share was 12.1% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
